Class DefaultButtonClickAction

java.lang.Object
  org.mt4j.input.gestureAction.DefaultButtonClickAction

Direct Known Subclasses:
DefaultSvgButtonClickAction
public class DefaultButtonClickAction
extends java.lang.Object
implements IGestureEventListener

Default clickgesture action for image buttons. Shrinks the shape upon pressing and scales it back to original size on releasing.

Author:
Christopher Ruff
